snippet.title: Ablaze - Cinematic Gameplay
snippet.description:
Get ready for an action-packed 2-player co-op adventure with Ablaze! Dive into clever puzzles, save adorable sheep, and confront the mischievous fire spirit, Scorch. 

Wishlist now on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1616420?utm_source=youtube_trailer_2&utm_campaign=none

Join our Discord:
https://discord.gg/J3RSEDEy4B
